      "text": "1. Deploy a fresh Exaix workspace and configure a test portal as described in the manual scenario.\n2. Submit a request and approve the generated plan.\n3. Run `exactl plan list` and `exactl plan list --status=approved`.\n4. Observe that no plans are listed, even though approval succeeded.\n5. Check the portal repo: the feature branch and changeset are present.\n6. Run `exactl changeset list`.\n7. Observe that no changesets are listed.\n\n## Expected vs Observed Behavior\n\n**Expected:**\n\n- Approved plans should be visible in `exactl plan list` (with or without status filter).\n- Created changesets should be listed by `exactl changeset list` after plan approval and execution.\n\n**Observed:**",
