    {
      "text": "1. **Changeset List Missing Config Portals**: The `exactl changeset list` command only scanned portal symlinks in the workspace but ignored portals defined in `config.portals`. Changesets in portal repositories defined only in config were not discovered.\n\n2. **Execution Loop Hardcoded Archive Path**: The execution loop used a hardcoded \"Archive\" path instead of the configured `config.paths.archive` value, causing plan archiving to fail or use incorrect locations.\n\n### Changes Made",
